### 5. Module 3: `src/modules/sketch/renderers/SnapOverlay.js` -- Visual Indicators

Follows the exact same imperative pattern as `DrawingPlaneOverlay.js` and `ExtrusionPreview.js`: a factory function returning an object with `group`, update methods, and `dispose`.

```javascript
